                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/4505" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-0641</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9059 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“长生”变“短命”，从内部控制看“疫苗之殇”</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">&quot;Longevity&quot; Becomes &quot;short-lived&quot;, Treating &quot;Vaccine Incidents&quot; From Internal Control</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">杨荟琳，张彧，胡艳梅，王杏芬</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">重庆工商大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">长春长生生物科技股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">医药卫生工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">质量管理部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">15 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">医药行业；“疫苗事件”；内部控制；企业风险</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">pharmaceutical industry; &quot;vaccine event&quot;; internal control; enterprise risk</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">长生生物自2018年7月“疫苗事件”爆发以来产生了许多不良后果，无论是对公司本身还是对公众生命安全都造成了极大的影响，引起国内外各界关注。其下场惨淡，先是被深交所决定终止上市；后是宣告其子公司长春长生破产。作为资本市场上首例因“重大违法”被退市的上市公司，其背后的原因具有特殊的研究价值和警示意义。本案例利用内部控制的五要素，深挖公司在高管设置、生产及销售控制活动、独立董事内部监督等方面的活动，复盘出其内部控制存在的缺陷。在其传统私有企业背景、涉及群众生命健康的行业背景下，该如何有效促进公司内部控制管理良好发展？找出内部控制缺陷后，从根本上进行杜绝是同类医药企业未来进行企业管理的一剂灵药。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Since the outbreak of the &quot;Vaccine Incident&quot; in July 2018, Changsheng has produced many undesirable consequences, which have had a great impact on the company itself and the safety of the public&#39;s lives, and have attracted attention from all walks of life at home and abroad. Its ending was bleak. It was first decided by the Shenzhen Stock Exchange to terminate its listing; then it declared bankruptcy of its subsidiary Changchun Changsheng. As the first listed company to be delisted on the capital market due to a &quot;significant violation of the law&quot;, the reasons behind it have special research value and warning significance. This case uses the five elements of internal control to dig deeper into the company&#39;s activities in senior management, production and sales control activities, internal supervision of independent directors, etc., to recap the defects in its internal control. In the context of its traditional private enterprise background and the industry background involving the life and health of the masses, how to effectively promote the good development of the company&#39;s internal control management? After finding the defects of internal control, fundamentally eradicating is a panacea for similar pharmaceutical companies to carry out enterprise management in the future.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2019</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《内部控制理论与实践》、《审计理论》、《公司治理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">内部控制</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020-06</td>
                            </tr>
